## 1. Feature Overview

The **Trip Map Tracking Portal** is a full-page dashboard that displays delivery trip routes on an interactive map. It supports both **single-trip** (detailed view) and **multi-trip** (overview) modes, with real-time vehicle animation playback, route color coding, and comprehensive trip analytics.

### Key Capabilities
- View all trips for a selected date on a single map
- Filter trips by session (Morning/Evening/All)
- Each route displayed with a **unique color** and numbered waypoint markers
- **Vehicle animation playback** — play, pause, forward, backward, reset with adjustable speed
- **Single trip mode**: detailed sidebar with timeline, financial summary, route stats
- **Multi-trip mode**: route list cards with enable/disable toggles per route
- Click a trip card in multi-trip mode to drill into single-trip detail
- Toggle numbered markers on/off
- Route deviation detection with alert

