Fetches all trips for the selected date on mount and whenever the date changes.

#### Control Bar Layout (MUI Grid)

| Column | Width | Component |
|--------|-------|-----------|
| Date Picker | `md={2.2}` | `@mui/x-date-pickers/DatePicker` |
| Session Filter | `md={1.8}` | `Select` — All / Morning / Evening |
