## 7. Bug Fixes Applied During Session

### Fix 1: Breadcrumb "Back" → Blank Page

| Item | Detail |
|------|--------|
| **File** | [menuCall.tsx](file:///c:/ASM%20Project/Git/ASM-Sales-React/Sales-web/src/utils/menuCall.tsx) |
| **Root Cause** | After page refresh, `menuItems.menuValue` is empty. Toggling an empty menu drawer = blank page |
| **Fix** | Check if `menuValue` is empty; if so, `router.push(paths.dashboard.root)` instead of toggling |
| **Impact** | All pages using `useHandleOpenLastMenu` hook benefit |

### Fix 2: Leaflet `removeLayer` Console Errors

| Item | Detail |
|------|--------|
| **File** | [trip-map-view.tsx](file:///c:/ASM%20Project/Git/ASM-Sales-React/Sales-web/src/sections/trip-creation/trip-map-view.tsx#L457-L510) |
| **Root Cause** | Cleanup called `control.remove()` which internally calls `this._map.removeLayer(...)`, but map was already null |
| **Fix** | Reordered cleanup (intervals → markers → controls → map), added per-control `try/catch`, guard on `control._map` |
| **Impact** | Eliminates all `Cannot read properties of null (reading 'removeLayer')` errors |

