## 8. Known Limitations & Future Improvements

| Area | Current State | Improvement Needed |
|------|--------------|-------------------|
| OSRM Server | Uses public demo server | Self-host OSRM for production reliability |
| Map Rebuild | Entire map rebuilds on filter/toggle change | Optimize to only update markers/polylines |
| Deviation Alert | Uses `alert()` popup | Replace with toast notification |
| Real-time Tracking | Playback of historical data only | Integrate live GPS API (e.g., Wheelseye) |
| Route Optimization | Routes shown as-is | Add optimized vs actual route comparison |
| Mobile Responsive | Desktop-first layout | Add responsive breakpoints for mobile |
